                                This page lists alternative Python implementations and specialized variants.
                                The reference implementation of Python is <strong>CPython</strong>, written in C and maintained
                                by the core development team. However, there are several other implementations that offer
                                different features, performance characteristics, or platform support.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-base-content/80">
